dialogueTree.title: René Arnoux: ""Wouldn't even pick it up, if my he..."
dialogueTree.english: "Wouldn't even pick it up, if my heart wasn't in it."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie wziąłbym się za to, gdybym tego nie czuł”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Не ўзяўся б за гэта, калі б гэтага не адчуваў».

dialogueTree.title: René Arnoux: ""So the wind is... yes, perfect.""
René Arnoux: ""Is my aim really *that* off?""
René Arnoux: ""Strange, I could have sworn...""
René Arnoux: ""I'm fine, just a little heart burn..."
dialogueTree.english: "I'm fine, just a little heart burn..."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nic mi nie jest, to tylko zgaga...”

dialogueTree.title: René Arnoux: ""Stop complaining and hurry up!""
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Перастань наракаць і каротка выкладай сваю думку!»

dialogueTree.title: René Arnoux: ""*Mon dieu*, how much can a man whi..."
dialogueTree.english: "*Mon dieu*, how much can a man whine, Gaston?"
dialogueTree.polish: „*Mon dieu*, ileż jeden człowiek może jęczeć, Gaston?”
dialogueTree.belarusian: «*Mon dieu*, колькі аднаму чалавеку можна ныці, Гастон?»

dialogueTree.title: René Arnoux: ""Don't get mayonnaise on the measur..."
dialogueTree.english: "Don't get mayonnaise on the measuring tape."

dialogueTree.title: René Arnoux: ""I feel 20 years younger every time..."
dialogueTree.english: "I feel 20 years younger every time it rains."
dialogueTree.polish: „Zawsze kiedy pada, czuję się 20 lat młodszy”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Заўсёды калі ідзе дождж, я адчуваю сябе на 20 гадоў маладзей».

dialogueTree.title: René Arnoux: ""It's a different game in the snow.""
dialogueTree.english: "It's a different game in the snow."

dialogueTree.title: René Arnoux: ""Build a solid routine and stick to..."
dialogueTree.english: "Build a solid routine and stick to it. That's all there is."
dialogueTree.polish: „Wypracuj sobie dobre nawyki i trzymaj się ich. Ot cała filozofia”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Выпрацуй добрыя звычкі і трымайся іх. Вось і ўся філасофія».
